#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:3
msgid "Please wait ..."
msgstr "Arhoswch os gwelwch yn dda ..."

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:7
msgid "Computing the new partitions ..."
msgstr "Yn cyfrifo'r rhaniadau newydd ..."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:11
msgid ""
"This probably happened because the selected drive or free space is too small "
"to be automatically partitioned."
msgstr ""
"Mae'n debyg digwyddodd hyn oherwydd mae'r gyrriant neu ofod rhydd a "
"ddewiswyd yn rhy fach i'w rhaniadu'n awtomatig."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:17
msgid "Automatic partitioning failed"
msgstr "Methodd rhaniadu awtomatig"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:17
msgid ""
"This probably happened because there are too many (primary) partitions in "
"the partition table."
msgstr ""
"Mae'n debyg digwyddodd hyn oherwydd mae gormod o rhaniadau (cynradd) yn y "
"tabl rhaniadau."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid "Choose how to partition:"
msgstr "Dewiswch sut i rhaniadu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:24
msgid ""
"This installer can automatically partition a drive for use by Debian, or if "
"you prefer, you can do it manually. If you do choose to automatically "
"partition a drive, you will still have a chance later to see the results, "
"customise it, and even undo the partitioning if you do not like it."
msgstr ""
"Gall y sefydlydd hwn rhaniadu disg ar gyfer ei ddefnyddio gan Debian yn "
"awtomatig, neu os hoffech, gallwch ei wneud e â llaw. Os ydych chi'n dewis "
"rhaniadu gyrriant yn awtomatig, cewch gyfle yn hwyrach i weld y "
"canlynniadau, eu addasu nhw, a hyd yn oed datwneud y rhaniad os nad ydych "
"ch'n ei hoffi."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid "Choose what to automatically partition:"
msgstr "Dewiswch beth i'w rhaniadu'n awtomatig:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:33
msgid ""
"If you select a whole drive, the automatic partitioning will remove or "
"resize existing partitions on the selected drive, which can cause data loss."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n dewis gyrriant cyfan, bydd y rhaniadu awtomatig yn dileu "
"neu'n ailfeintio rhaniadau sy'n bodoli eisioes ar y gyrriant dewisiedig, "
"sy'n gallu achosi colled data."

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:41
msgid "Partitioning scheme:"
msgstr "Cynllun rhaniadu:"

#. Type: select
#. Description
#: ../templates:41
msgid ""
"The drive can be partitioned in one of several different schemes. If you are "
"unsure, choose the first one."
msgstr ""
"Mae nifer o gynlluniau rhaniadu gwahanol ar gael er mwyn rhaniadu'r "
"gyrriant. Os nad ydych chi'n siwr, dewiswch yr un cyntaf."

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:47
msgid "Unusable free space"
msgstr "Gofod rhydd ni ellir defnyddio"

#. Type: error
#. Description
#: ../templates:47
msgid ""
"Automatic partitioning failed because the chosen free space may not be "
"used.  There are probably too many (primary) partitions in the partition "
"table."
msgstr ""
"Methodd rhaniadu awtomatig oherwydd ni ellir defnyddio'r gofod rhydd "
"dewisiedig. Mwy na thebyg, mae gormod o rhaniadau (cynradd) yn y tabl "
"rhaniadau."

#. Type: string
#. Description
#: ../templates:60
msgid "Automatically partition a drive"
msgstr "Rhaniadu gyrriant yn awtomatig"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:64
msgid "Use the largest continuous free space"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r gofod rhydd parhaol mwyaf"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#. for example "Use entire drive: IDE0 master - Maxtor 46L489"
#: ../templates:69
msgid "Use entire drive: ${DEVICE}"
msgstr "Defnyddio'r gyrriant cyfan: ${DEVICE}"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:73
msgid "Manually edit partition table"
msgstr "Golygu'r tabl rhaniadau â llaw"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:77
msgid "Automatically partition the free space"
msgstr "Rhaniadu'r gofod rhydd yn awtomatig"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:81
msgid "/, /home and swap"
msgstr "/, /home a gofod cyfnewid"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:85
msgid "/, /usr, /usr/local, /var, /var/mail, /tmp, /home and swap"
msgstr "/, /usr, /usr/local, /var, /var/mail, /tmp, /home a gofod cyfnewid"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:89
msgid "All files in one partition (recommended for new users)"
msgstr "Pob ffeil ar un rhaniad (argymhellir ar gyfer defnyddwyr newydd)"

#. Type: text
#. Description
#: ../templates:93
msgid "Separate partition for the home directories"
msgstr "Rhaniad ar wahan ar gyfer y cyfeiriaduron cartref"

#~ msgid "Partition with custom settings"
#~ msgstr "Rhaniadu gyda gosodiadu addasiedig"
